\par\plain \ilvl0{\listtext	\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf7 \uc0\u8226 	}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf7 The founder of the nonprofit organization, Marcus Chamberlain, has entrusted Sarah to organize 2 separate New Year's Eve parties. One for his donors, and one for all of the volunteers that have tirelessly worked throughout the year to assist his nonprofit.<!$Scr_Ps::5><$Scr_Ps::4>}
