\par\plain \ilvl0{\listtext	\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf7 \uc0\u8226 	}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf7 Sarah was working up to last-minute, and didn't have time to change she was wearing a well fitted double-breasted designer white skirt suit. She put her hair in a ponytail to keep their art arise so she could focus on her laptop.<!$Scr_Ps::5><$Scr_Ps::4>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\li346\fi14\sb60\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf8 - Visual descriptors:<!$Scr_Ps::4><$Scr_Ps::5>}
\par\pard\plain \tx235\tx720\li936\fi-216\sl262\slmult1\ltrch\loch \ls3\ilvl0{\listtext	\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf7 \uc0\u8226 	}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf7 In part, to show that while Evan was being respectful and patient, there was a part of him that really wanted to pull Sarah away from her work. He decided to take a detour to a neighborhood famous for holiday decorations before heading to Liz's. Although reluctant, Evan insisted Sarah take a 10-minute break and enjoy the decorations. She did take a 10-minute break, smiled, and pretended to be interested, but all the while, her mind was preoccupied with work that needed to get done. }
