\par\pard\plain \tx235\tx720\li576\fi-216\sa120\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch \ls6\ilvl0{\listtext	\f2\fs22\b0\i0 \uc0\u8226 	}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0 <$Scr_Ps::6>Even though there wouldn't be a lot of specified dialogue, you can convey to the reader that Evan pretty much talked the whole trip. All of his words were focused on what a great three-day visit this was going to be and how excited he was that they would be celebrating their first Christmas together as a couple.<!$Scr_Ps::6>}
