\par\pard\plain \tx235\tx720\li576\fi-216\sa120\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch \ls4\ilvl0{\listtext	\f2\fs22\b0\i0 \uc0\u8226 	}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0 <$Scr_Ps::6>The scene ended with their arrival at the parking lot of Liz's apartment complex. The end of the scene should reflect Evan's enthusiasm that they had arrived, with Sarah's unspoken and hidden desire that the ride would have lasted last longer so she could have gotten more work done. She had promised Evan she wouldn't work much during their trip - only emergencies and minimal email replies.<!$Scr_Ps::6>}
